snippet.title: FNF: Turnabout ~ An FNF one-shot (FC)
snippet.description:
WARNING: This mod has a few flashing lights, so, to be safe, don't watch or play it if you suffer from epilepsy. OBJECTION!! Phoenix Wright fights in court using the power of funk, against Miles Edgeworth, in the pursuit of a Not Guilty Verdict!
----------------------------------
OBJECTION!!! God I just started scrolling on GameBanana's FNF new page and I saw this uploaded SECONDS ago. Ace Attorney is one of my favorite franchises of all time so this was a blessing from the gods themselves.
----------------------------------
Mod link: 
https://gamebanana.com/mods/528041
----------------------------------
